The '''RMF-31''' was a heavy floor-mounted [[Repeating blaster cannon/Legends|repeating blaster cannon]] that could be rotated and/or elevated to fire in different directions depending on where the enemy was coming from. During her search for [[Kyle Katarn]], [[Mara Jade Skywalker|Mara Jade]] might have come across this weapon.

